    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you\u2019d think this beauty just rolled off the showroom floor today\u2014it is absolutely spotless and runs like a total dream! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in basically perfect shape and ready for some fun adventures, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
