    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and remains in absolute showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and fragrant, showing no bolster wear or sun fading. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; I possess a comprehensive binder containing every service record performed by certified master technicians. No leaks, no rattles, and no deferred maintenance\u2014just a pure, responsive driving experience. If you are seeking a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new driver, this is the finest example available.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
